  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "OBRIX through Aquatic Chain — thematic resonance: OBRIX is the Coral Reef engine. Reef FDN reverb wraps OBRIX brick synthesis in the spatial context that matches its identity. Fathom Character 0.15 (deep emphasis) amplifies the low-mid body of OBRIX's dual-source architecture. Drift at 4 voices gives the two sources (Pulse + Saw) an ensemble width they could not have with just unison detune. Tide in AutoFilter at 0.12 Hz — the reef environment breathes. Reef at size 0.65, density 0.7. The chain is not adding effects to OBRIX — it is placing OBRIX in the environment it belongs to.",
